                real-time seat availability, and payment processing.
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
            <h3>Next Steps for Your Project</h3>
            <p>Once your basic site is on GitHub, consider these enhancements:</p>
            
            <div class="step">
                <div class="step-number">1</div>
                <div class="step-content">
                    <h4>Add JavaScript Functionality</h4>
