                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="step">
                <div class="step-number">3</div>
                <div class="step-content">
                    <h4>Add Backend functionality</h4>
                    <p>Consider using services like Firebase for database and authentication capabilities.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="step">
                <div class="step-number">4</div>
